race.description: Hip Pocket Workwear & Safety Grafton Handicap (Bm66)
race.comment: LA CACHE A VIN (8) gone to a new level this prep with the three wins from his last five starts. Rounded them up effortlessly with the 56kg when saluting over 1183m at this track. Well placed and there is no reason he cannot score again in this stronger contest. SOOBOOCO (2) big class drop when he shouldered the 60.5kg for a tough on-pace fourth over 1100m at Armidale. Will roll forward again with the senior rider hopping on. Each-way. CABSAV (4) has a good record on his home track and can improve sharply at his third run back. Battled on fairly with the 60kg when sixth over 1100m at Armidale. Leading player from the low draw. TRYANZA (9) another suited on his home track who gets weight relief today. Sat on the good tempo with the 60.5kg when a narrow fifth over 1183m at this track. Can stalk the good tempo and figure prominently.
